    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "ALLEGHENY\nAFFEREN\nUSAIR\nTimetable Supplement\nEffective October 28, 1979\nNew\nGolden\nSun Service\nto Florida!\nSave up\nto 50%\nUSANR",
      "There's\na change\nin the air...\nMore service\nto Arizona!\nStarting October 28, USAir introduces new\nGolden Sun Service to and from Tucson...\n• Cleveland-Tucson (new direct service)\n• Pittsburgh-Tucson (new direct service)\n• Phoenix-Tucson (new nonstop service)\nUSAir's new service to Tucson includes\nthe only direct service from Cleveland, and\nafternoon direct service from Pittsburgh, and\nevening nonstop service from Phoenix.\nAnd to Phoenix USAir offers:\n• Buffalo-Phoenix (direct service)\n• Newark-Phoenix (direct service)\n• Minneapolis / St. Paul-Phoenix (nonstop\nservice)\n: Pucson phoenix ions serie\nAlso starting October 28, USAir will intro-\nduce First Class service, in addition to our\nregular Coach service, on selected flights to\nPhoenix.\nNew Golden Sun Service\nadds\nmore\nto your flight to the sun. More... like com-\nplimentary wine before departure and hot\ntowels to relax and refresh you. Seat selec-\ntion is standard on Golden Sun Service.\nFor details on our new service and wide\nrange of discount fare plans, see your travel\nagent or call USAir.\nWe fly where the sun shines best.\nUSAIR\n2015,034.004"
    ],
